org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.bpm

Class Loop

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.bpm.Activity
      • org.wiredwidgets.cow.webapp.client.bpm.Loop

  • public class Loop
extends Activity
    A special list of Activity objects where, when finishing, a user can choose whether or not to repeat the actions or to continue in the workflow. Loops have a slightly altered XML format, where the Task representing whether or not to continue looping is called a loopTask. The loopTask, however, is identical to the XML format of a normal Task.
    Author:
    JSTASIK
